import React from 'react'
import { BrowserRouter } from 'react-router-dom'

import Header from './components/header'
import Footer from './components/footer'

import Routes from './routes'

import './App.css'

function App(){
  return (
    <BrowserRouter>

      <Header/>
  
      <Routes/>


      <Footer/>
    </BrowserRouter>
  )
}

export default App
